title: Sidewall, 1810–20
creditline: Gift of The Museum at The Fashion Institute of Technology
description: Drapery paper with lace floral motifs and green clover design in center. Bunches of fabric on either edge. Foliate swags on far edges of paper. Printed in shades of gray, white and green on off-white ground.  c. 1810.

tombstone.epitaph:
Sidewall, 1810–20.
1810–20. Block-printed on handmade paper. Gift of The Museum at The Fashion Institute of Technology. 1998-75-203.
